            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
          You Will Never Be The Same After Reading This Book
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-primary-100">
          If the persecution does not affect you, the squirting certainly will!
        </p>
